data.description: Welcome to this country-quiet home on 1.1 acres in Avon Grove School District.  Two additional rooms could easily be bedrooms, making a total of 4 bedrooms.  Beautiful & peaceful yard that backs to wooded land.  Inside you’ll find some historic features dating back to the 1800’s, including an original stone fireplace, large wood beams, and built-in cupboard.  You’ll enjoy the modern updates that have been done: eat-in kitchen, main floor mud room / laundry room, propane gas heating, and solar panels.  This property needs much TLC, but could really shine for someone with vision.  Close to Route 1 and 896 for easy access to local conveniences.  Make your appointment today!
